sentences: In 2007, Beal moved to Albuquerque, New Mexico.
In 2012, Beal signed a recording contract with Hot Charity, an imprint of independent record label, XL Recordings.
Beal's first single for the labels, "Evening's Kiss" was released on February 17, 2012, and the accompanying music video was illustrated by Beal.
Beal's debut album, entitled Acousmatic Sorcery was released on April 2, 2012.
